<dl id="n08125m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08125m">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08125m"> 125(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> even animal / generation abhorred / fish allowed</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Generation was abhorred by the Albigenses even in the animal kingdom. Consequently, abstention from all animal food, except fish, was enjoined. <small> <a name="CECRA" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CECRA"><cite title="source">&ldquo;Coemgen&rdquo;, &ldquo;Rosary&rdquo; and &ldquo;Albigenses&rdquo;</cite></a> <cite a>Catholic Encyclopaedia</cite></a> (1911) I, &lsquo;Albigenses&rsquo; 268a</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
